casebody.data:
Avon Neal McKINLEY
v.
Judy SILLS, Manager - Combined Records NC Department of Correction. No. 143P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 21, 2006. Avon Neal McKinley, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 17th day of March 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Franklin County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 21st day of March 2006."
